{
  "title": "Smack",
  "children": [
    {
      "title": "Overview",
      "lines": [
        "Loop glitcher for",
        "live audio.",
        "",
        "Grabs a quantized",
        "loop of whatever is",
        "upstream, slices it,",
        "and rolls seeded",
        "random FX plus a",
        "new slice order.",
        "",
        "The pattern repeats",
        "each pass until you",
        "re-roll it.",
        "",
        "Works in chain slots",
        "and Master FX."
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Quick Start",
      "lines": [
        "1. Set Loop Len.",
        "2. Play something.",
        "3. Hit Capture to",
        " grab the last",
        " loop length.",
        "4. A/B to punch",
        " between clean",
        " and pattern.",
        "5. Re-Roll for a",
        " new pattern.",
        "",
        "Or: Arm, then play.",
        "Recording starts on",
        "the next step and",
        "stops after the",
        "loop length."
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Knobs",
      "children": [
        {
          "title": "Chain UI Knobs",
          "lines": [
            "In the chain editor",
            "knobs 1-8 are:",
            "",
            "1: FX Density",
            "2: Order Density",
            "3: Loop Length",
            "4: Slice Res",
            "5: Wet",
            "6: Pitch Range",
            "7: Fill Amount",
            "8: Seed",
            "",
            "Quantize is on the",
            "Setup knob page."
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "Knob Pages",
          "lines": [
            "On Master FX and",
            "the param pages:",
            "",
            "Main: Loop Len,",
            " Slice Res, FX",
            " Density, Order.",
            "",
            "Perform: Capture,",
            " A/B, Re-Roll,",
            " Clear (Arm is in",
            " the list).",
            "",
            "Fill: Fill on/off,",
            " Fill 1x, Fill Amt.",
            "",
            "Setup: Wet, Pitch",
            " Range, Quantize,",
            " Seed, Transport."
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Pads & Steps",
      "lines": [
        "Bottom-left pads:",
        "",
        "Capture: retro-grab",
        " (green)",
        "Arm: record next",
        " step (red)",
        "A/B: clean loop or",
        " pattern (white)",
        "Re-Roll: new",
        " pattern (blue)",
        "Clear: drop loop",
        " (orange, above",
        " Capture)",
        "Fill: tap latches,",
        " hold = momentary",
        " (yellow, above",
        " Arm)",
        "",
        "Hardware Capture",
        "button: retro-grab.",
        "",
        "Steps 1-16 show the",
        "slice pattern, one",
        "color per effect,",
        "white is playhead.",
        "Press a step to",
        "mute its effect;",
        "press again to",
        "restore it.",
        "",
        "While Fill is on",
        "the steps show the",
        "fill pattern."
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Effects",
      "lines": [
        "22 slice effects:",
        "",
        "retrigger, reverse,",
        "pitch (varispeed),",
        "half/double speed,",
        "gate chop, buzz,",
        "bitcrush, repeat",
        "after split, reverse",
        "after split,",
        "tape stop and start,",
        "vinyl scratch,",
        "envelope shapes,",
        "pan tricks, filter",
        "sweeps, vowel",
        "filter, tonal delay,",
        "granular freeze,",
        "synced delay and",
        "ping-pong,",
        "distortion, phaser,",
        "gated reverb.",
        "",
        "FX Density sets how",
        "many slices get an",
        "effect; Order sets",
        "slice reshuffling."
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Fill",
      "lines": [
        "Fill is a temporary",
        "pattern variation,",
        "like Elektron fills.",
        "",
        "A second seeded",
        "pattern, biased",
        "toward stutters,",
        "sounds only while",
        "Fill is on; the",
        "main pattern is the",
        "\"not fill\" side.",
        "",
        "Fill pad (yellow):",
        "tap latches Fill,",
        "tap again to stop;",
        "hold plays it only",
        "while held.",
        "",
        "Fill knob page:",
        "Fill: on/off latch.",
        "Fill 1x: fill to",
        "the end of this",
        "pass, then off.",
        "Fill Amt: how busy",
        "the fill gets.",
        "",
        "Fill works over the",
        "A side too, and",
        "follows Quantize.",
        "Re-Roll and Seed",
        "change the fill",
        "pattern with the",
        "main one."
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Seed & Re-Roll",
      "lines": [
        "Seed browses",
        "patterns by number:",
        "the same seed always",
        "gives the same",
        "pattern.",
        "",
        "Re-Roll varies the",
        "current seed for a",
        "fresh pattern; dial",
        "the Seed knob to",
        "return to the",
        "canonical one."
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Sync & Transport",
      "lines": [
        "Set Move's MIDI",
        "Clock to Out so",
        "Smack locks to the",
        "transport (same as",
        "the Arp).",
        "",
        "Without it, Smack",
        "free-runs at the",
        "project tempo.",
        "",
        "Transport (Setup):",
        "Follow: Move stop",
        "pauses the loop,",
        "play restarts it.",
        "Free: keep looping."
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Presets",
      "lines": [
        "Module presets save",
        "all knobs, the seed",
        "and re-roll state,",
        "plus slice mutes.",
        "",
        "Audio is not saved:",
        "capture a new loop",
        "after loading."
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Screen Reader",
      "lines": [
        "With the screen",
        "reader on (Global",
        "Settings), the chain",
        "editor announces",
        "pads, knob changes",
        "and loop state."
      ]
    }
  ]
}
